Quickstrike:



It still didn't make sense to what Black Arachnia was saying, but he 
tried to listen. From her tone and behavior, she was getting mad at 
him. He didn't want that. He tried to make up for his lack of 
understanding. 

He twitched the two strips of metal at his cheeks then nodded to her.
